Simple evolution, has nothing to do with personal taste. The ones who try riskier stuff are going to die more often. A kid bothers you at the wrong minute, your cat jumps on the keyboard, power outage, group member decided to go mental, random numbers just go the wrong freaking way -- things you could survive in a super-safe environment but are just going to be too much in anything riskier. Eventually the oldtimers are the ones who played it safe, a few rare exceptions aside.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aauminki>Aauminki</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 158<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/10/03 5:41:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26442.topic&index=19>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hardcore server??</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>non Zekkers thought in a majority that Sullon was insane and a bad idea.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->SZ was a great idea, just like prisons it serves to keep the worst loonies away from the normal crowd. <p><big><center><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370955 target=blank>Sage Aauminki Iceblade</a><br><a href=http://www.vazaelle.dk target=blank>Caer Cadarn</a></big><br>Vazaelle Server</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub