<br>
This is exactly the kind of person I had in mind.  Ultimatly it wouldnt matter if Sony even changed one thing, I really think people would get a kick out of seeing how far they could get, even with current blue server rules. <br>
In reality I think they WOULD have to change some things if they wanted people to stay and play a lot on the server... but I think people underestimate how crazy some people are, and how much time they have on thier hands hehehe<br>
As far as making it PvP, that would substantially increase the risk involed to the point where I dont think many people would even get past level 10-15. If people werent able to at least get into the low 50s in level I doubt many would think it was worth thier time.  Might be a hoot though. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
