<br>
New rule, you would get an automatic resurect if you are level 10 or below.  Consider it to be your old &quot;master&quot; who you studied under as an apprentice keeping an eye on you after you've gone out into the world.  But have this only happen if you turned in your newbie note initially.<br>
<br>
The guild system would then mean something, since you'd join a guild just for protection.<br>
