<br>
The way EQ is right now, the game would be impossible as a hardcore server with 1 death and that's it.<br>
<br>
EQ is far too big and too long with far too many bosses to do such a thing, unless you are to retune the hell out of every encounter and jack up the exp by multiple factors of 10 per kill, you're not going to do much.<br>
<br>
With a 10 min rez timer at least it separates the men from the boys when you go do an encounter you'd better be ready. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=545853" target="top">Thallan Berzerk - 62 Cleric on Xev</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
